sources.description:
YOU DAMN WELL WON’T FORGET HIM!
A decorated Vietnam Vet returns to his father’s ranch in Arizona just as criminally minded carnies begin to cause trouble.

Directed by Daniel Vance
Writers: Daniel Vance, Mike Nolin
Stars: Steve Sandor, Rockne Tarkington, Richard X. Slattery
Genres: Action, Drama
